ghost &lt;unk&gt; is a 1944 american comedy film directed by george archainbaud and written by robert creighton williams . the film stars lon chaney , jr. , mary beth hughes , don " red " barry , george " gabby " hayes , anne jeffreys , george " gabby " hayes , anne jeffreys , lon chaney , jr. . the film was released on march 31 , 1944 , by republic pictures .